					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7948089#post-4344386</guid>
				<title>Staff Post - Open</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7948089/scp-3828#post-4344386</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2019 03:02:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Elogee FishTruck</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4037075</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The first image that was used in this article is non-compliant with the SCP wiki's license, as it originates from <a href="https://www.gns.cri.nz/Home/Learning/Science-Topics/Ice-Snow/Gallery/Antarctica-Gallery/Weddell-seal">here</a>, and can only be used for &quot;private and non-commercial use&quot; according to the <a href="https://www.gns.cri.nz/Home/Contact-Us/Disclaimer-and-Copyright">Copyright Information</a>, making it non-compliant. The second image is cc-compliant, as it originates from <a href="https://www.mapsland.com/world/arctic-region/detailed-political-map-of-arctic-region-1995">here</a> which is licensed under CC BY-SA 3.0 according to the <a href="https://www.mapsland.com/copyright">Copyright Information</a>. As such, the first image has been removed, while the second image remains.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
